		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>The lack of respecs will seriously shortern the life-span of this game for me. It's fun, and I enjoy it, but I will *not* be rolling another Summoner and levelling them up just to try out a demon focussed build instead of my elemental focussed build I'm using now. <br />
<br />
I'm also petrified that spending points on agility &amp; strength (only a few) to wear gear will kill me long term because of the willpower requirements for summoning elementals...</div>
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
